{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~kobsa/courses/ICS104/course-notes/cscw-problems.htm", "content": "<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN\">\n<html><head><title>Problems in CSCW</title>\n\n\n\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1\"></head><body bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" text=\"#000000\">\n<p><big><font size=\"+3\"><big><b><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">Key \nproblems in CSCW</font></font></b> </big></font></big></p><p><big>&nbsp; \n</big></p><p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+2\"><big>1. In any type of\n      meeting:</big></font></font>\n</big></p><blockquote><big>\n  </big><p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+1\"><big>\"Channel\n  limitations\"</big></font></font><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+1\"><big><br>\n\n        <font size=\"3\"><big><big>(In face-to-face conversations, the meaning of a message\n        is transported as follows [Mehrabian 1972]: 7% verbally, 38% para-verbally\n        (intonation,\n        volume) and 55% non-verbally (facial expression, gestures, body language))</big></big></font></big></font></font></big></p><big>\n  </big></blockquote>\n<p><big>\n</big></p><p><big>&nbsp;\n<br>\n<font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+2\"><big>2. In multi-party\nremote meetings:</big></font></font> \n</big></p><blockquote><big>\n  </big><p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+1\"><big>- Turntaking (audio delay, video angle, \n          lack of peripheral/sublimal awareness...):<font face=\"Monotype Sorts\" size=\"6\"><big><big><br>\n \n          <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">&nbsp; </font></big></big></font></big></font><font size=\"6\"><big>&nbsp;</big></font></font><font size=\"6\"><big>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</big></font><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"6\"><big><font face=\"Monotype Sorts\">&nbsp;</font></big></font><img style=\"width: 50px; height: 36px;\" alt=\"Finger pointing right\" src=\"../../../graphics/pointing-finger-right.jpg\"></font><font size=\"6\"><big> </big></font><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+1\"><big>strict floor control</big></font></font>\n  </big></p><big>\n  </big><p><big>&nbsp;<font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+1\"><big>- \n  Lack of immersion</big></font></font> </big></p><big>\n  </big></blockquote>\n<p><big>&nbsp; \n<br>\n<font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+2\"><big>3. \nIn multi-party physical meetings with remote members:</big></font></font> \n</big></p><blockquote><big>\n  </big><p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+1\"><big> \n    - Same as above, for remote members</big></font></font> </big></p><big>\n  \n  </big><p><big> - <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><big>Social\n        \ndynamics changes </big></font> \n  <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><big><a href=\"HTML%20Presentation%20folder/sld001.htm\"><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></a></big></font></font></font></font></big></p>\n  <p><br>\n  </p>\n  <big>\n  </big></blockquote>\n<p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+2\"><big>4. In 1 on 1 conferencing\n      \n(but also multi-party)</big></font></font> \n</big></p>\n<blockquote><big>\n  </big><p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"+1\"><big>Eye contact</big></font></font> <font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><big><a href=\"netmeeting.jpg\"><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The linked image shows a computer-based videoconferencing system (namely Microsoft's Netmeeting)\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></a></big></font></font></font></font></font></font><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><br> \n&nbsp;</font> \n  </big></p><big>\n  </big></blockquote>\n\n</body></html>", "encoding": "ascii"}